1.In the sequence: gunzip pluto-xx.tar.gz ，tar xvf pluto-xx.tar 
2.Config : definition.h pluto.ini
3.In .basrc: export PLUTO_DIR= ...  . Then python ...
4.Need gcc
5.GUIpython: Need tk (sudo apt-get install tk-dev)
	     Need matplotlib (need freetype(sudo apt-get install libfreetype6-dev libxft-dev),png(sudo apt-get install libpng-dev)) 
             Need scipy (need las pack fortran：sudo apt-get install libblas-dev liblapack-dev gfortran)
6.In BashOnWindows GUI need Xming: DISPLAY=:0 GUI_pyPLUTO.py。(DISPLAY=:0 后可以接任何可视化的东西)
            